            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini amen. Anno nativitate eius millesimo centesimo
                        nonagesimo tertio, quinto idus februarii, indictione undecima. Ex huius
                        evidentis intrumenti pateat recitatione quod nos, <persName
                            ref="#people/3226">Castracanis</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3214">Uberti</persName> et <persName><name ref="Agletina"
                                >Agletina</name></persName> coniux eius et filia quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Ghiselmus">Ghiselli</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Acconcialeo">Acconcialeone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertellus">Ubertellus</name></persName>
                        germani et quondam <persName><name ref="Castraleo"
                            >Castraleonis</name></persName>, (…) ubi interfuit notitia Francessci
                        iudicis ordinarii et notarii (…) omnes quatuor simul vendimus et tradimus,
                        cedimus atque mandavimus tibi <persName><name ref="Artoldus"
                                >Artaldino</name></persName>, ospitalario domus Altepascensis de
                            <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Roads"
                            >Puteo</placeName>, ementi et recipienti pro domino <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandino</name></persName> rectore <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >ospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName> (…) unam nostram terre petiam
                        positam in confinibus Putei et in loco qui vocatur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Oil #Fruits/vegetables">le Plana</placeName>,
                            <rs key="#Oil">olivas</rs> et <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">ficus et
                            ceteras arbores</rs> in se habentem. Et tenet unum caput in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, aliud caput tenet in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Manens">Manentis</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Lucterius">Lucterii</name></persName>
                        germanorum et quondam <persName><name ref="Gratianus"
                            >Gratiani</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Rumacchius"
                                >Rumacchi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Vecchio"
                                >Vecchi</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Alioctus"
                                >Aliocti</name></persName> quondam et filii quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lanfrancus">Lamfranci</name></persName> et in terra <persName
                            ref="#people/3217">Aldimarii</persName>. Ambo latera tenet in terra
                        suprascripti ospitalis Altepascensis. Item cedimus et mandavimus tibi
                        suprascripto emptori omnia iura et actiones et proprietates utiles et
                        directas (…) pro pretio octocentum viginti solidorum bonorum denariorum
                        pisane nove monete. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupli. Actum aput
                            <placeName ref="#places/3234">Rosaiolum</placeName>, presentibus
                                <persName><name ref="Mainectus">Mainecto</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bei">Bei</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Fabbrus">Fabro</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Bello">Belli</name></persName> et <persName ref="#people/3240"
                            >Ugolino</persName> filio <persName key="#Viscount" ref="#people/3239"
                            >Orlandini <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs></persName> rogatis <rs
                            key="#Witness">testibus</rs>. (S) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Judge"
                                ><name ref="Franciscus">Franciscus</name></persName> domni
                        imperatoris <rs key="#Judge">iudex ordinarius</rs> et <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> post traditam scripsi, complevi et dedi.</ab>
                    <ab>Rerum gestarum series ideo litterarum fidei commendatur, ne ipsarum veritas
                        in posterum memorie subtrahitur, et per hoc sequitur secutura posteritas
                        quod futuris temporibus enitenter appareat. Castracanis quondam Uberti
                        inquisivit Aldimarium et <persName><name ref="Sardus"
                            >Sardum</name></persName> per tres vices et plus si ipsi vellent emere
                        ab eo suprascriptam terre petiam quam dicebat se velle vendere ospitali de
                        Altepascio. Et illi responderunt quod non poterant emere, et quia non
                        habebant denarios unde emerent dictam terram, et dederunt eidem Castracani
                        licentiam vindendi ospitali Altepascensi et cuicumque sibi placeret. Quod
                        actum est coram <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3210"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> Sancti Petri de Puteo</orgName>,
                        presentia et testimonio Mainecti et <persName><name ref="Fornarius"
                                >Fornarii</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Teudiscus"
                                >Tedissci</name></persName> et Fabri filii Belli rogatorum testium,
                        anno nativitate eius millesimo centesimo XCIII, quinto idus februarii,
                        indictione undecima.</ab>
                </div>
